summary.label:
The event application for festival-goers provides essential features to help you organise your experience of the Festival, and a chance to experience the 2022 event as if you were there!

In 2022, find out more about the free and bilingual (French & English) Festival de Cannes app for smartphones and tablets:
-	Exclusive announcements and all the latest news, complete with media clips, and regularly updated on the Official Selection, the juries, the events and the awards.
-	Hourly coverage of the event in news and interviews to be shared on social networks;
-	Videos of the red carpet, photocalls, press conferences, interviews...
-	Permanent access to the Festival TV channel;
-	Trailers and film extracts;
-	Daily photo galleries;
-	Services dedicated to accredited professionals: programming, session bookmarks, access to online ticketing, geolocation and practical information. 
-	Notifications and customisation features to experience the Festival at your own pace.

Please note: use the password-protected access dedicated to journalists to display content and features reserved for the Press.
